			<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=111311&amp;sid=9963e97b7767f20618cfb558e6fe2e7f#111311"><img src="templates/eqluclin/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Fri Apr 01, 2005 4:43 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Re: Supreme Court hearing P2P case</span></td>
				<td width="30%" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap" align="right"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=111311&amp;sid=9963e97b7767f20618cfb558e6fe2e7f"><img src="templates/eqluclin/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>     </td></tr></table></td>
